<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Type-Matching code completion</b></p><p>When there's an array of the expected type in the context, invoke the Type-Matching code completion (<span class="shortcut">&shortcut:SmartTypeCompletion;</span>) twice. The IDE will suggest getting an element from this array.</p></body></html>